########## DESIGN ##########




http://localhost/api/get/[data name]/?param=value


########## FUNCTIONS ##########

REQUEST_ACCESS (HTTPS)

    This function can be used for sign in, sign up and get new access token.

    If there's no record of this user in the system, it will automatically
    create a new account based on the information received.

    If the device id is unrecognized, it will automatically register this
    device id.

    Requires
    - email address
    - password
    - device id
    - app secret

    Optional
    - app id

    Returns
    - access token

